  "slug": "pickable-health-orbs",
  "title": "Pickable Health Orbs",
  "description": "Ever wanted RPG styled configurable pickups? Here they are!",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/d6e0a8f200546ab339f8f6ca25d199f0.png\" alt=\"PIckable Health Orbs banner\" width=\"1142\" height=\"524\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/ZyNGZr4E2u\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/879788820265074698?color=F7F3F5&amp;labelColor=030B14&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Discord&amp;label=Discord&amp;logoColor=ff96c5\" alt=\"\" width=\"194\" height=\"28\" /></a><a href=\"https://github.com/cojalexandru/pickable-orbs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/PICKABLEORBS-GitHub?color=F7F3F5&amp;labelColor=030B14&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=GitHub&amp;label=GitHub&amp;logoColor=ff96c5\" alt=\"\" width=\"214\" height=\"28\" /></a><a href=\"https://wiki.decursioteam.com\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Website-DecursioTeam-F7F3F5?labelColor=030B14&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"\" width=\"208\" height=\"28\" /></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/5b267057e5289aa3818c50860385b947.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1044\" height=\"58\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">OVERVIEW</span></strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;We, at <strong>The Decursio Team</strong>, want to present to you today, one of our first mods, called <strong><em>Pickable Health Orbs!</em></strong>&nbsp;This is an RPG style mod which adds orbs that can be dropper by certain mobs/blocks. When picked up, these orbs will provide certain benefits, such as instant healing and other potion effects.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">If you're a modpack developer, you might be happy to hear that, unlike other mods, this one uses entities to create these orb. This means that situations where a player would be able to pick up an orb and use it for later, will not happen. However, if you're interested exactly in the behavior described previously, know that, starting with one of the future versions, it will be possible to pick up an use the orbs for later, if that's what you want.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/5b267057e5289aa3818c50860385b947.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1044\" height=\"58\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">FEATURES</span></strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">This mod is <em><strong>highly configurable</strong></em>. This means that you can add/remove any orbs you want through the mod's config file.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Additionally, you can customize the drop chance of every orb, which mobs should drop them, their effect duration, their effect amplifier and more.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">By default, this mod features a number of 8 pickable orbs. Let's see them:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">- <em><strong>Healing: </strong></em>When picked up, it will heal the player by a flat amount (which can be configured)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">-&nbsp; <em><strong>Poisonous</strong></em>: Will inflict the Poison effect for 5 seconds by default</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">- <em><strong>Damaging:</strong></em> This is mainly the \"Instant Damage\" effect from the Vanilla Minecraft - It will give two hearts of damage</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">- <strong><em>Jumping:</em></strong> Will give the Jump Boost effect for 5 seconds by default</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">- <strong><em>Speedster</em>:</strong> Gives the speed effect for 5 seconds</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">- <strong><em>Confusion:</em></strong> Inflicts Blindness for 5 seconds</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">- <strong><em>Levitation:</em></strong> Will allow the player to levitate for 5 seconds</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">- <strong><em>Fire Resistance:</em></strong> Provides Fire Resistance for 5 seconds</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Again, all the values mentions before can be altered through the mod's config file which can be found in <strong><em>instance/config/pickableorbs/orbs</em>.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/5b267057e5289aa3818c50860385b947.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1044\" height=\"58\" /></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>IMAGES</strong></span></em></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/441/145/1lbkvw9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1115\" height=\"627\" /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/441/146/gj0zlc8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1115\" height=\"627\" /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/441/147/2022-03-17_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1115\" height=\"628\" /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/441/148/2022-03-17_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1115\" height=\"627\" /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/441/149/2022-03-17_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1115\" height=\"628\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/5b267057e5289aa3818c50860385b947.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1044\" height=\"58\" /></p>",
